==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ti-]]'' (demonstrative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-am]]'' (correlative suffix of time)

===Correlative===
'''tiam'''

# [[then]], at that time (demonstrative correlative of time)
#: As with other demonstrative correlatives in Esperanto, ''[[tiam]]'' can be combined with ''[[ĉi]]'', the adverbial particle of proximity, or with ''[[for]]'', the adverbial particle of distance. ''Tiam ĉi'' thus means ''then [recently or soon]'' and ''tiam for'' means ''then [long ago or in distant future]''.

